  <div id="text-content_28E22BF0-1CA1-0135-6E66-22000B5A851D" class="text-block-content">
    <p>You can create sub-accounts in Canvas. Sub-accounts help establish your account's hierarchical structure and house courses and enrollments. Sub-accounts can be created manually or via <a href="/t5/Admin-Guide/How-do-I-import-SIS-data-to-a-Canvas-account/ta-p/98" target="_blank">SIS import</a>.</p>
<p><a href="https://community.canvaslms.com/t5/Video-Guide/Account-Structure-Admins/ta-p/383798" target="_blank">View a video about Sub-Accounts</a>.</p>
  </div>
</div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="open_account" data-step-uuid="7fa2f4eb-c427-4c66-b19b-ff859773698e">
    <h2 id="open_account" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Open Account</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/007/949/740/original/167b4d34-2e3f-4046-9aed-39673e67bdab.png" srcset="" alt="Open Account" height="542" width="453">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_28E2E6B0-1CA1-0135-6E68-22000B5A851D" class="text-block-content">
    <p>In Global Navigation, click the <strong>Admin</strong> link [1], then click the name of the account [2].</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="open_sub_accounts" data-step-uuid="35F30099-DEB4-4902-B850-601974C2610F">
    <h2 id="open_sub_accounts" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Open Sub-Accounts</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/005/794/247/original/fbdbc322-1ccf-4d95-82c7-b843c7cbcac9.png" srcset="" alt="Open Sub-Accounts" height="299" width="167">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_28E32100-1CA1-0135-6E6A-22000B5A851D" class="text-block-content">
    <p>In Account Navigation, click the <strong>Sub-Accounts</strong> link.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="show_accounts" data-step-uuid="BED45623-1F95-4FC5-B792-CCE2892CD52E">
    <h2 id="show_accounts" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Show Accounts</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/000/792/274/original/039f3bc2-2f49-45a1-be10-2164450b8f85.png" srcset="" alt="Show Accounts" height="68" width="519">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_28E35BF0-1CA1-0135-6E6C-22000B5A851D" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Click the <strong>down arrow</strong> to show sub-accounts.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="add_sub_account" data-step-uuid="43CCCAFF-02AF-4319-AB49-3D9F0B4905C9">
    <h2 id="add_sub_account" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Add Sub-Account</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/001/470/312/original/d339bf78-2298-4171-84bf-c0444e2e1a72.png" srcset="" alt="Add Sub-Account" height="311" width="525">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_28E39370-1CA1-0135-6E6E-22000B5A851D" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Click the <strong>Add</strong> button.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="title_sub_account" data-step-uuid="BF559F54-BF32-4E03-977D-CDDCB30AD970">
    <h2 id="title_sub_account" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Title Sub-Account</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/000/792/278/original/bf81bbd8-0ffe-4bd6-84b4-9a171a138459.png" srcset="" alt="Title Sub-Account" height="368" width="528">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_28E3CAF0-1CA1-0135-6E70-22000B5A851D" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Enter a title for the sub-account in the title field. Press <strong>Return</strong> (on a MAC keyboard ) or <strong>Enter</strong> (on a PC keyboard).</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

